      "content": "**Architecture:**\n1. **OpenClaw Gateway**: Port 18789 (local)\n2. **NGINX Reverse Proxy**: Port 443 (HTTPS) → Port 18789\n3. **DNS**: entrosana.com → 18.225.98.79 (EC2 public IP)\n4. **SSL**: Let's Encry",
